---
// Home B2B callout — owner-operated / travel-partner positioning
---

<section id="partners" class="relative overflow-hidden border-t border-gold/10" style="background:#0e1a0e;">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none">
    <div class="w-2/3 h-2/3 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-10" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse, #c9913a 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-20 lg:py-28 text-center">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6 reveal">
      <span class="h-px w-10 bg-gold/40"></span>
      <p class="font-sans text-[13px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-gold-light">For Travel Partners</p>
      <span class="h-px w-10 bg-gold/40"></span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-ivory font-light tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6 reveal reveal-delay-1">
      A boutique <em class="italic text-gold-pale">B2B charter partner</em>
    </h2>

    <p class="font-sans text-base md:text-lg text-warm-gray font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 reveal reveal-delay-2">
      We own and operate our fleet — VEDA 1 to 4 — so you work directly with the people delivering the experience.
      No brokers, no intermediaries: consistency, flexibility, and a shared commitment to excellence, journey after journey.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <a href="/our-philosophy" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-gold hover:bg-gold-light text-white font-sans text-xs tracking-ultra uppercase px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300">
        Read Our Philosophy
        <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/contact" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border border-white/25 hover:border-gold text-white/80 hover:text-gold font-sans text-xs tracking-ultra uppercase px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-gold/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
        Become a Partner
        <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
